@startuml CompositeStructure_PaymentGateway_Detailed
!$target = %getenv("PLANTUML_TARGET")
!include .plantuml/_base.puml
!include .plantuml/_targets/$target.puml

title "Payment Gateway — detailed composition"

component "Payment Gateway" {
  port "pay-in"     as PI
  port "pay-out"    as PO
  port "events-out" as EO

  [Router]      as R
  [Authorizer]  as A
  [Anti-Fraud]  as F
  [Settlement]  as S
  [Audit Log]   as AL

  PI --> R
  R  --> A
  A  --> F : checks
  A  --> S : on success
  A  --> PO : denied
  S  --> PO : approved
  S  --> AL : audit trail
  AL --> EO : settlement.posted
}

note bottom of F : Anti-fraud is colocated with the gateway in this deployment;\nin a federated model it would sit outside the boundary.
note right of S : PCI-DSS scope ends here; audit log is post-settlement.
@enduml
